metric_definitions.allocated_effort_to_date: Allocated Effort (To Date) is the sum of allocated hours recorded in allocation daily rows within the reporting period (2025-03-16 → 2026-01-23) across all included projects.
metric_definitions.actual_effort_to_date: Actual Effort (To Date) is the sum of actual hours recorded in allocation daily rows within the reporting period (2025-03-16 → 2026-01-23) across all included projects.
metric_definitions.variance_hours: Variance (Hours) = Allocated Effort (To Date) − Actual Effort (To Date).

notes: All totals in this export are derived from resource_allocation_daily within the selected reporting period.
